node.text:
It's almost ready... 📸📕😈 After months of intensive work I can finally say it 😁 Actually it's already prepared, selected, edited and built in a digital format, the only thing left - is to wait until it's getting printed as well, because (as I mentioned) I want it to be made in the best quality, so it takes much more time and resources to be created 😅 But anyway, the hardest part is already behind me and I can proudly say that my ArtBook is going to be unforgettable 😉 hope it will not take more than few weeks till the release... 😋
P. S. How do you like my home office businesslady look? 😁

#ootd #blacktights #officelook #highheels #artbook #photography

node.text:
Finally ready to announce the project I've been working on for the last half an year - my EXCLUSIVE PHOTO BOOK! 📕🔥 Some of you already know that the shooting part is almost done, so now the only things are left are to finish the writing part, make the photo order and to build the coffee table book itself (layout) 😉 The book is going to contain about 170 unpublished on any of my platforms,extra seductive and provocative (yet tasteful and aesthetic) photos in the highest quality along with autobiographical stories about me and my way, printed on hq glossy pages🥰(of course the digital version will be available too). It's going to be an absolutely different level of experience for you and for me as well 😉 Stay tuned, the release will be soon! ❤️🔥
#bikinisiren #pool #bikini #redhead #ukrainiangirl
